default improve the margins on the farm and will encourage processors to invest in British milk fields.
defaultd)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultBuilding trust within the supply chaindefault - identified as the most significant factor in the fresh produce sector, this could be addressed by retailers and processors supporting producers with clear and transparent pricing arrangements, longer term contracts, responsible promotional activities and support of British produce through in-store and online campaigns.
